<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Anthony Train Station</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #eaeaea;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #eaeaea;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Anthony Train Station</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear valued {{passengers}},</p>
            <p>We extend a warm welcome to all our passengers arriving at Anthony Train Station!</p>
            <p>We are delighted to have you on board, and we want to remind you that the departure time for the train is just 8 minutes away. Please ensure that you are ready and have all your belongings with you.</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Train Departure Details:</strong><br>
                Station: Anthony Train Station<br>
                Departure Time: [Insert Departure Time]<br>
                Platform: [Insert Platform Number]
            </p>
            <p>As we embark on this journey together, we kindly request everyone to be mindful of their fellow travelers and follow the train station's safety guidelines.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or require any assistance, our friendly station staff will be more than happy to help you.</p>
            <p>We wish you a pleasant and comfortable journey with us. Thank you for choosing Anthony Train Station for your travel needs.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Team at Anthony Train Station</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Contact Information: [08161778965 for passenger inquiries]</p>
            <p><a class="button" href="#">Visit our website</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
